{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a mystical journey as Savitri and Satyavan, two characters destined to become Twin Flames. In this enthralling turn-based puzzle adventure, you'll guide them through a beautifully stylized low poly world, navigating a hexgrid filled with obstacles and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084560/extras/SteamGIF_074.gif?t=1736661675\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Challenge Your Mind:</strong> Test your strategic thinking with a variety of brain-teasing puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Connect with a Friend: </strong>Join forces with a friend in local co-op mode to tackle the game's challenges together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Forge a Bond:</strong> Experience the power of love and connection as you guide Savitri and Satyavan towards their ultimate goal.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Local Co-op Mode:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience Twin Flames with a friend in local co-op mode, where you'll work together to solve puzzles and navigate the hex grid. This mode enhances the gameplay experience, fostering a deeper connection between players as they work together to achieve the Twin Flame state.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Join Savitri and Satyavan on their quest to become Twin Flames. Explore, strategize, and connect in this captivating puzzle adventure.</u></strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084560/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736661675","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084560/page.bg.jpg?t=1736661675","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstat